# ProgressBar

⚠️ **Deprecation warning** ⚠️

This component has been deprecated and is no longer maintained. We recommend using the `loader` component instead.

## Installation & Import

```bash
yarn add @ids-ts/progress-bar
```

```tsx
import { ProgressBar } from '@ids-ts/progress-bar';
```

## Props

> **Deprecated** — Use the `loader` component instead.

| Prop | Type | Required | Description |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| `value` | `number` | Yes | Current progress value. |
| `max` | `number` | Yes | Maximum progress value. |
| `counterElement` | `ReactNode` | No | Custom counter element displayed above the bar. |
| `isReversed` | `boolean` | No | Reverses the fill direction when true. |
| `automationId` | `string` | No | Test automation identifier. |

