## Usage Patterns

### Basic

```tsx
({ value, max }) => (
  <div style={displayWidthStyle}>
    <ProgressBar
      automationId="basicUsage"
      value={value}
      max={max}
      counterElement={
        <Counter max={max} value={value} automationId="basicCounter" />
      }
    />
  </div>
)
```

### Custom Counter

```tsx
({ value, max }) => {
  return (
    <div style={displayWidthStyle}>
      <ProgressBar
        automationId="basicUsage"
